image_analysis.description: A photograph of a bedroom interior. The room features a large bed with white linens and an orange/tan tufted headboard. To the right of the bed is a light wood nightstand with a black lamp. In the background, there are two white doors; one is partially open with a small white label attached to it. To the right of the doors is an orange chair and a dark wood desk. On the floor, which has yellow carpeting, there is a red circular object and a rolled-up green mat. The walls are off-white with crown molding.

Bates-style watermark/identifier 'EFTA00000308' in bottom right corner
